<div id="wrapper"><h2><a href="/output/Page2.asp"><img alt="" height="70" src="../files/images/XM_logo.gif" title="XM London Digital Communication" width="162" /></a></h2><h2><img width="129" alt="About us" height="80" border="0" src="/files/images/XM_L2About_shdr.gif" /></h2><p><br />XM London is part of OgilvyAction and in turn part of WPP, one of the worlds largest communication groups. This means that although we are a small company we understand large companies.</p><p>We subscribe to all group policies in respect of best practice. In particular compliance with Sarbanes Oxley regulations and financial compliance.</p><p>As part of WPP we have as core values honesty, integrity and respect for people. These core values determine the way we approach business and they define the principles in which we expect our people to behave in the conduct of our business.<br /><br />We recognise the importance of high standards of social, ethical and environmental behaviour. Being a responsible citizen is not only the right thing to do, it also adds to our success. For more please visit <a href="http://www.wpp.com" target="_blank">www.wpp.com</a></p><p>Over the past decade, the quality of our work has been recognised, both by numerous <a href="/output/Page27.asp">industry awards</a>, and by the length of time our clients stay with us. </p><p>As part of a major communications group we really understand brands and their development and how best to leverage them in the online environment.</p><p>We also have access to a global range of research and have OgilvyAction offices across the world which means that, if you need data or informed comments from these markets as to what is going on we can quickly access this information.</p><img class="hide" src="/files/images/clear.gif" width="1" height="1" alt="" />
